import requests

headers = {
    "User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) "
                  "AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) "

}

</span><span class="last">Campuses</span></p>\n</nav>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><h1 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"><div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained">\n<p><strong>Classes close to you.</strong> Austin Community College has 11 campuses conveniently located across Central Texas. Every campus offers a variety of classes and support services like libraries, learning labs, and computer labs. ACC&#8217;s three destination campuses also provide extended services and hours of operation. They are Highland Campus (central), Round Rock Campus (north), and Riverside Campus (south).</p>\n\n\n\n<div style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;height:20px" aria-hidden="true" Transportation</strong></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Most campuses are accessible by public transportation. ACC offers the Green Pass. You can ride Capital Metro bus or rail FREE. Parking permits are available for students who prefer to drive to campus. <div class="wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><h1 class="has-text-align-left wp-block-post-title" style="padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-bottom:0;">Campuses</h1></div>
<div class="wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)"></div>
<main class="wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"><div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained">
<p><strong>Classes close to you.</strong> Austin Community College has 11 campuses conveniently located across Central Texas. Every campus offers a variety of classes and support services like libraries, learning labs, and computer labs. ACCs three destination campuses also provide extended services and hours of operation. They are Highland Campus (central), Round Rock Campus (north), and Riverside Campus (south).</p>
<div aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;height:20px"></div>

</div>

<p>Let us show you around campus and give you a feel for the ACC student experience. Our recruitment team can provide a personal or group tour at many of our campus locations.</p>

<p><strong>Parking &amp; Transportation</strong></p>
</div>
<p>Most campuses are accessible by public transportation. ACC offers the Green Pass. You can ride Capital Metro bus or rail FREE. Parking permits are available for students who prefer to drive to campus. If you have a green car, special parking options are available.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.austincc.edu/students/parking-and-transportation"><strong>Learn More</strong></a></p>

<p><strong>Sustainability</strong></p>
</div>
<p>ACC is a leader in sustainability with initiatives in reducing energy consumption, increasing recycling, and also promoting carpooling and mass transit alternatives.</p>
<p><a href="https://offices.austincc.edu/energy-and-sustainability/" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><strong>Learn More</strong></a></p>

<p><strong>Safety &amp; Security</strong></p>
</div>
<p>The ACC Police Department is among the largest and best trained agencies in the region. Officers patrol each campus and work with the Office of Emergency Management to keep our community prepared and informed in the event of a crisis.<a href="https://offices.austincc.edu/operations-and-public-affairs/acc-police-department/" rel="noopener" target="_blank"></a></p>
<p><a data-id="https://offices.austincc.edu/operations-and-public-affairs/acc-police-department/" data-type="link" href="https://offices.austincc.edu/operations-and-public-affairs/acc-police-department/" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><strong>Learn More</strong></a></p>

<script id="wp-block-template-skip-link-js-after">
	( function() {
		var skipLinkTarget = document.querySelector( 'main' ),
			sibling,
			skipLinkTargetID,
			skipLink;

		// Early exit if a skip-link target can't be located.
		if ( ! skipLinkTarget ) {
			return;
		}

		/*
		 * Get the site wrapper.
		 * The skip-link will be injected in the beginning of it.
		 */
		sibling = document.querySelector( '.wp-site-blocks' );

		// Early exit if the root element was not found.
		if ( ! sibling ) {
			return;
		}

		// Get the skip-link target's ID, and generate one if it doesn't exist.
		skipLinkTargetID = skipLinkTarget.id;
		if ( ! skipLinkTargetID ) {
			skipLinkTargetID = 'wp--skip-link--target';
			skipLinkTarget.id = skipLinkTargetID;
		}

		// Create the skip link.
		skipLink = document.createElement( 'a' );
		skipLink.classList.add( 'skip-link', 'screen-reader-text' );
		skipLink.id = 'wp-skip-link';
		skipLink.href = '#' + skipLinkTargetID;
		skipLink.innerText = 'Skip to content';

		// Inject the skip link.
		sibling.parentElement.insertBefore( skipLink, sibling );
	}() );
	
</script>

\n\n\t\t\t\t<div id="post-800" class="post-800 page type-page status-publish hentry">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-content" id="main-content">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Procurement opportunities with the Austin Community College District (ACC) are listed below. Submissions are publicly opened on the submission deadline.</p>\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Submission Requirements</h2>\n<p>ACC uses Workday Strategic Sourcing (WSS) for the proposal process. To log in to WSS, click on the solicitation number below. Once logged in, you can access all solicitation documents and submit your proposal.</p>\n<p>If you require assistance logging into or creating a WSS account, please contact the appropriate <strong>Solicitation Contact</strong> or <a href="mailto:p2p@austincc.edu">p2p@austincc.edu</a>.</p>\n<p>[<strong>N.B.:</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Only submissions made via WSS by the submission deadline will be accepted.]</strong></p>\n<p>Please direct any questions or requests for additional information to the individual(s) listed as the contact for the solicitation. This includes proposals eligible for the&nbsp;<a href="https://offices.austincc.edu/business-services/procure-to-pay/small-business-development-program/">Small Business Development Program (SBDP)</a>.</p>\n<p>Procure to Pay (P2P) does not monitor or record visits to this page. You are responsible for monitoring this site for updates or addenda to a posted solicitation.</p>\n<p>Please click on the solicitation number to view documents in WSS.</p>\n<p>\n<table id="tablepress-1" class="tablepress tablepress-id-1 tablepress-responsive">\n<thead>\n<tr class="row-1">\n\t<th class="column-1">Issue Date</th><th class="column-2">Solicitation</th><th class="column-3">Solicitation Contact</th><th class="column-4">Submission Deadline (Must be received by noon CT, unless otherwise noted)</th><th class="column-5">Status</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class="row-striping row-hover">\n<tr class="row-2">\n\t<td class="column-1">01/16/2026</td><td class="column-2"><strong>REQUEST FOR PROPOSALS (RFP)</strong><br />\nDistrict-Wide Commercial Water Delivery Systems Repair Services and Parts, Indefinite<br />\nDelivery, Indefinite Quantity (IDIQ)<br />\n<a href="https://us.workdayspend.com/rfps/public/1043329"> #890-26-264-00-S-JG-RFP</a></a></a><br />\nSOLICTATION CONFERENCE<br />\nACC will host an optional virtual solicitation conference on Wednesday, Febuary 4, 2026 at 1:30<br />\np.m. CST via ZOOM Virtual Meeting. <div class="col-xs-12">
<h1>Advertised Solicitations</h1>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12">
<!-- ADD BANNER PHP -->
<div id="page-banner">
</div>
<!-- END -->
</div>
<!-- Begin Page Menu Widget Loop -->
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-9">
<div class="post-800 page type-page status-publish hentry" id="post-800">
<div class="entry-content" id="main-content">
<p>Procurement opportunities with the Austin Community College District (ACC) are listed below. Submissions are publicly opened on the submission deadline.</p>
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Submission Requirements</h2>
<p>ACC uses Workday Strategic Sourcing (WSS) for the proposal process. To log in to WSS, click on the solicitation number below. Once logged in, you can access all solicitation documents and submit your proposal.</p>
<p>If you require assistance logging into or creating a WSS account, please contact the appropriate <strong>Solicitation Contact</strong> or <a href="mailto:p2p@austincc.edu">p2p@austincc.edu</a>.</p>
<p>[<strong>N.B.:</strong><strong>Only submissions made via WSS by the submission deadline will be accepted.]</strong></p>
<p>Please direct any questions or requests for additional information to the individual(s) listed as the contact for the solicitation. This includes proposals eligible for the<a href="https://offices.austincc.edu/business-services/procure-to-pay/small-business-development-program/">Small Business Development Program (SBDP)</a>.</p>
<p>Procure to Pay (P2P) does not monitor or record visits to this page. You are responsible for monitoring this site for updates or addenda to a posted solicitation.</p>
<p>Please click on the solicitation number to view documents in WSS.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-default" id="programs-services" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0">Meet Your Campus</h2>
<p style="padding-bottom:64px">Cypress Creek Campus is nestled among the trees and trails in Cedar Park, just north of Austin. Enjoy shady breezeways and a laid-back campus experience in the center of one of Texass fastest-growing cities. Diverse classes, high-tech labs, and a vibrant community helps make Cypress Creek home for many ACC students.</p>
<div class="wp-block-group has-contrast-3-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-fdb8975a wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="border-radius:10px;padding-top:64px;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:64px;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)">
<div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">

<div class="wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-default" id="programs-services" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0">Wellness Walking Path</h2>
<p>ACC has wellness walking paths on three campuses: Cypress Creek, Northridge, and South Austin Campus. Enjoy exercise and fresh air along the new scenic path at Cypress Creek campus. Take time to explore nature and relax in the natural beauty of Cypress Creek. <a data-id="https://storymaps.arcgis.com/stories/5cdf30c5d79e4be98289e75addc3f3e0" data-type="link" href="https://storymaps.arcgis.com/stories/5cdf30c5d79e4be98289e75addc3f3e0" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">Find Your Walking Path</a></p>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-default" id="programs-services" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0">Programs &amp; Services at ACC Cypress Creek</h2>
<p>Students can enroll in career-technical classes or choose from a variety of general education courses that easily transfer to universities. We also provide a full range of support services, including a library, a learning lab with free tutoring, and an <a href="https://students.austincc.edu/testing-services/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">ACC testing center</a> for TSI Assessments, challenge exams, and more.</p>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-default" id="4-find-the-program-for-you" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0">Cypress Creek Campus Highlights</h2>
<p class="has-text-align-left">Austin Community College offers more than 100 programs in 10 areas of study that lead to career certificates, associate degrees, bachelors degrees, or university transfer. Explore classes that can boost your income, improve your skills, and change your life.</p>
<div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-658170e2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">

<h5 class="wp-block-heading">University Transfer</h5>
<p>Our affordable core curriculum credits and programs transfer easily and count toward your bachelors degree. ACCs supportive learning environment and transfer guidance ensures you get where you need to be.</p>

<script id="wp-block-template-skip-link-js-after">
	( function() {
		var skipLinkTarget = document.querySelector( 'main' ),
			sibling,
			skipLinkTargetID,
			skipLink;

		// Early exit if a skip-link target can't be located.
		if ( ! skipLinkTarget ) {
			return;
		}

		/*
		 * Get the site wrapper.
		 * The skip-link will be injected in the beginning of it.
		 */
		sibling = document.querySelector( '.wp-site-blocks' );

		// Early exit if the root element was not found.
		if ( ! sibling ) {
			return;
		}

		// Get the skip-link target's ID, and generate one if it doesn't exist.
		skipLinkTargetID = skipLinkTarget.id;
		if ( ! skipLinkTargetID ) {
			skipLinkTargetID = 'wp--skip-link--target';
			skipLinkTarget.id = skipLinkTargetID;
		}

		// Create the skip link.
		skipLink = document.createElement( 'a' );
		skipLink.classList.add( 'skip-link', 'screen-reader-text' );
		skipLink.id = 'wp-skip-link';
		skipLink.href = '#' + skipLinkTargetID;
		skipLink.innerText = 'Skip to content';

		// Inject the skip link.
		sibling.parentElement.insertBefore( skipLink, sibling );
	}() );
	
</script>

    lambda x: f'<a href="{x}" target="_blank">{x}</a>'
)
